data.description: Welcome to this spacious remodeled Cape Cod home with a thoughtfully designed addition, situated in a desirable location with NO HOA!  The property boasts a fenced back yard ensuring privacy and security, complemented by newer vinyl siding, a 10 year old roof, and replaced windows  for enhanced comfort and efficiency.  Step inside to discover the charm and elegance of re-finished hardwood floors throughout. The main level features an expansive extended primary bedroom offering ample closet space and a full bathroom for convenience. Enjoy gatherings in the generously sized family room flooded with natural light, alongside a separate dining room perfect for entertaining.  The kitchen is a chef's delight, complete with additional space in the rear leading to a large deck overlooking the serene backyard, featuring a retaining wall. Upstairs, two large bedrooms with hardwood floors await, accompanied by a fully remodeled bathroom.  The basement presents an opportunity for an in-law suite or additional living space, boasting a separate entrance with a sidewalk on the side. This level includes two legal bedrooms, a kitchen, and a family room.  Outside, soak in the tranquility of the private backyard with its captivating views. With its versatile layout and abundance of amenities, this home caters to the needs of a large family and is ready for immediate occupancy. Don't miss out on this exceptional opportunity – schedule your showing today! SHOWINGS WILL ONLY TAKE PLACE ON 2/7/24 - 2/13/24 DUE TO TENANT IN PROPERTY. NO EXCEPTIONS WILL BE MADE. HOUSE WILL BE REMOVED FROM THE MARKET ON 2/13/24 AND BACK ON AT THE END OF MARCH IF NOT UNDER CONTRACT BEFORE THEN.
